          <p>Every mystery box hides a trio pulled from the <b>Cheeselads</b> selection of over 170 artisan cheeses, aged in-house at Tyrwhitt Road. Nobody knows their lineup until they open the box, and no two drops repeat it. These are living cheeses with short shelf lives, which is exactly why you collect them fresh in your chosen hour.</p>
